Walt,<br><br>
The site is here, and still active, and it has grown. Thanks for your post. We all share in everyone's grief. It is a difficult road when the ability to speak the words comes so very hard. We all have feelings for our fallen brothers, even if we did not know them. They were once a part of us all in some way. We survived to carry their memory, and that is an honorable and noble thing to do. In some ways, they will live on.<br><br>
